00:29:14.111 --> 00:29:17.238
Bob, how are you doing?
How's the wife treating you?

405
00:29:26.957 --> 00:29:28.416
Easy.

406
00:29:28.500 --> 00:29:30.584
Keep it moving.

407
00:29:33.381 --> 00:29:34.631
Red...

408
00:29:54.653 --> 00:29:58.864
