429
00:32:20.340 --> 00:32:22.466
He never said who did it.

430
00:32:22.550 --> 00:32:25.594
But we all knew.

431
00:32:28.932 --> 00:32:31.809
Things went on like that for a while.

432
00:32:31.893 --> 00:32:34.520
